reviews.reviewText: Like another reviewer mentioned, the fabric is on the thinner side. It isn't super smooth either. But overall I'd rate the quality high for the price. The zippers look delicate. Packaging was nice and the bags arrived quickly and in good condition. Happy with these bags for now.
